com.interpss.simu
Interface SimuContext

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
SimuContextImpl
public interface SimuContext
extends NameTag

A representation of the model object 'Network'. Simulation context class

The following features are supported:

  • Net Type
  • Resource Type
  • Msg Hub
  • Aclf Net
  • Acsc Net
  • DStability Net
  • Dist Net
  • Opf Net
  • Loadflow Algorithm
  • Simple Fault Algorithm
  • Dyn Simu Algorithm
  • Dclf Algorithm

See Also:
SimuPackage.getSimuContext()
